I have been following this thread with interest. I wanted to get closer to the date before committing. Now that I have a soft schedule I would like to invite myself if OK with you veterans. Is it the 4th at St Nicks, no wings, or is it what Loonietoons suggested quote:  "What no one else.. same old same old well at least we know who wants to GTG lets set date for Friday April 11 say around 8 or Saturday April 12 or any other date"  Or is it at the 477 Wing without wings or Buffalo Wings on Centennial Parkway, formerly Highway 20, sometimes still is.  And when is it, the 4th, 8th, 12th or as Loonietoon suggested " any other date". Man you guys are getting me confused which has been really easy as the big six O approaches so stealthily.
